Extent of thyroidectomy: When should hemithyroidectomy be performed? 
Recommendations from the Francophone Association for Endocrine Surgery, the 
French Society of Endocrinology and the French Society of Nuclear Medicine.

Deguelte S(1), Colas PA(2), Guerin C(3), Leboulleux S(4), Najah H(5), Lifante 
JC(6).

